Package: rightwatching
Title: A shiny app to visualize far-right incidents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Christoph', 'Trost', email = 'chris@toph.eu', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: A shiny app to fetch data of far-right violent incident, contextualize and visualize them. Can be used to visualize any sort of violent incidents.
